  "texts": [
    "The algorithm utilizes an Encoder-Decoder model combined with Byte Pair Encoding (BPE) to manage the vocabulary size and eliminate unknown words, while processing both monolingual corpora concurrently to leverage shared linguistic features.",
    "The algorithm of training unsupervised machine translation as in Fig. 3 below, (1) Append the monolingual corpora to one corpus.",
    "(2) Apply BPE tokenization on the resulting corpus.",
    "(3) On the same corpus, learn token embedding as in 10.",
    "(4) Learn two language models the first one to translate."
